{
  "id": "59285b7dba093700118fa1e2",
  "title": "ブレストの道具",
  "created": 1495817086,
  "updated": 1506931905,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2582",
      "text": "ブレストの道具",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2583",
      "text": "参加者25人でのブレスト開催時にどんな道具があると良いかについて相談された時に書いたリストです",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2584",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2585",
      "text": "\t大きい[ポストイット](75mm x 75mmなど)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1506931905
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2586",
      "text": "\t\t書いて壁などに貼り複数人で共有する用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2587",
      "text": "  1人に1個行き渡る個数",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2588",
      "text": "  \t他人が持っているからという理由で意見が抑制されないように。意見表明のハードルは可能な限り取り除く。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2589",
      "text": "  色が選べるなら単色(黄色)で揃えると良い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495910388
    },
    {
      "id": "5929c7f4aff09e0000962419",
      "text": "  選べないなら色を混ぜても良いが、色分けに意味を持たせる人とそうでない人が混在すると思考に負担がかかる。事前に話し合いが必要。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495910388,
      "updated": 1495910495
    },
    {
      "id": "5929c85eaff09e000096241a",
      "text": "  色分けに意味をもたせるなら各人が全色を待たずに使えるようにしなければならない。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495910495,
      "updated": 1495910512
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da258a",
      "text": " 大きいポストイット用のペン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da258b",
      "text": " \tボールペンでは壁に張り出した時に離れて読めないため、太いペンが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495910518
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da258c",
      "text": "  たとえばこういうの https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B001MT8802/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da258d",
      "text": "  マッキーでもいいけど油性なので机にしみるリスクがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da258e",
      "text": "  最低で黒が1人に1本行き渡ること。余裕があれば赤と青もあるとベター。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da258f",
      "text": " 小さいポストイット(38mm x 50mmなど)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2590",
      "text": " \t個人が手元で使う想定のサイズ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2591",
      "text": "  \t壁用の75x75は手元で使うにはスペースを食いすぎるため",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "5929c88eaff09e000096241b",
      "text": "   並べるとA4のプリント用紙に25枚貼ることができる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495910542,
      "updated": 1495910633
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2592",
      "text": "   1人2個(200枚)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2593",
      "text": " \thttp://www.mmm.co.jp/office/post_it/list01/653rp.html",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2594",
      "text": "\t手元の筆記用のボールペン",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2595",
      "text": "\t たとえばこういうの https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B001C09BS4/",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2596",
      "text": "  各人が自分の使いやすいペンを持参するのが良いが、インクが切れたりペンを共有したいケースが起きたりするので人数分のペンがあると良い。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2597",
      "text": " A4プリント用紙100枚入り1個～3個",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2598",
      "text": " \t潤沢な白い紙として。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da2599",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da259a",
      "text": "その他、あると良いことがあるかもしれないが、なくても良いもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da259b",
      "text": " どこでもホワイトボードになるシート https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B004BEJ9MG",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da259c",
      "text": " ホワイトボードマーカー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da259d",
      "text": " \t会場に備え付けと言われても信用してはいけない、インクが切れてたりする。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495910669
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da259e",
      "text": "\t粘土",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da259f",
      "text": " 段ボール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a0",
      "text": " レゴブロック",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a1",
      "text": " ハサミ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a2",
      "text": " ガムテープ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a3",
      "text": " 養生テープ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a4",
      "text": " ビニール紐",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a5",
      "text": " 割り箸",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a6",
      "text": " 竹串",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a7",
      "text": "\t巻き尺(長さを測る用)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a8",
      "text": " カッターナイフ、カッターマット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25a9",
      "text": " 色数の多い色鉛筆",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25aa",
      "text": " 両面テープ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7eaff09e0000da25ab",
      "text": " アロンアルファ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495817086
    },
    {
      "id": "59285b7dba093700118fa1e2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1495817086,
      "updated": 1495910677
    }
  ]
}